  Constrain 4 1 roll 3 copy -0.0279 mul exch 1.999 mul add exch
  -0.9844 mul add Constrain 5 1 roll -0.2891 mul exch -0.5338 mul add
  exch 1.91 mul exch add Constrain 3 1 roll} def
